#### Optimized Builds

**On Unix (Linux/MacOS) with x86 CPUs:**

```sh
RUSTFLAGS="-C target-cpu=x86-64-v3" cargo install {{project-name}} -F mimalloc
```

**On Windows with x86 CPUs:**

```powershell
$env:RUSTFLAGS="-C target-cpu=x86-64-v3"
cargo install {{project-name}} -F mimalloc
```


